choices.text:
Write an email to my boss letting them know I am leaving the company
Subject: Notification of Resignation 
Dear [Boss's Name], 
I wanted to let you know that after much consideration, I have decided to resign from my position at [Company Name]. My last day will be [Date]. 
I am grateful for the opportunity to work with such a great team and company. Thank you for your support during my time here. 
Please let me know if there is anything else I can do before leaving. 
Sincerely, 
[Your Name]
